name: Lalafell
description:
My very first Lora upload. I created this to give back to the community and to experiment to see if a Lalafell could be created from prompts. Use without the term "lalafell" since most models are trained on lalafell fanart which usually are low quality or 'chibi' versions of characters with the wrong proportions. I trained this using AnyloraCheckpoint_novaeFp16Pruned.

Use weights 0.7-1.0 for best results.

modelVersions.name: v1.5
modelVersions.description: Initial release version. I created a 1.0 for private use then redid everything on it.
